      "instruction": "Wash twice with 100 µL washing buffer. Washing buffer is PBS with the detergent Tween-20."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Incubate for 00:10:00 ."
    },
    {
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Add 100 µL blocking buffer. Blocking buffer is PBS with BSA (bovine serum albumin) and is used to prevent unspecific binding."
    },
    {
